page.title: 09TWO TYPICAL HOMES.
page.content:
{THREE BEDROOMED BUNGALOW (built 1969) The 'Ryan' bungalow is quite large with three large bedrooms. There is a through lounge into the dining area. The kitchen is quite spacious with many wall units, washing machine and cooker. There is gas central heating, large gardens front and back and an attached garage.
{FOUR BEDROOMED HOUSE (built 1969) The 'Lyric' semi detached house has on the ground floor a cloakroom,toilet and long lounge/dining room and kitchen. Upstairs in the bedrooms are linen cupboards and two bedrooms have fitted wardrobes.The bathroom has a low line bath and pedestal basin. There are gardens front and rear and an integral garage.The first buyer could choose what heating method he wanted.
